Apple Says Iphone Is Not Logging Location

-- B y   B i l l   K o e n i g
-- 
2011-04-27T12:40:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-27/apple-defends-iphone-s-location-services-says-users-aren-t-being-tracked.html
(Corrects name of company in first paragraph.)  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  said it’s not
“tracking the location” of users’ iPhones. The quote was part
of a question-and-answer format release by Apple.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
